  Contribute
  ==========

  We are happy about everybody who helps contributing.
  The following should help you and us with your contribution:

  * Please follow the [Code of Conduct](#{page_path('code_of_conduct')}).
  * We are located in IRC on freenode.net in the [#ruby-community](irc://irc.freenode.net/#ruby-community) channel.
  * You can find a [list of core contributors here](#{page_path('contributors')}).
  * Fork the repository on [https://github.com/apeiros/ruby-community](https://github.com/apeiros/ruby-community)
  * Provide your contributions as [Pull Requests](https://help.github.com/articles/using-pull-requests/)
  * We use bootstrap, sass and slim
  * The file suffixes are .yaml, .markdown and .html.slim
